90% of Menu is less than $10.  Counter Service.  Simple, real meal & ingredients in a different kind of Drive-In.  No Sauces. 😜  Sea Salt, Pepper, Mayo and Ketchup {the only acceptable fake} are the only condiments used and available. 😁  $8.79 RIBEYE SANDWICH was delish! Perfect temp medium ribeye, Mayo with bunch of lettuce and decent, just right tomatoes.  FREE WATER CUP available upon request! 👏  Available HOT GIARDINIERA retail only has 100+mg Sodium (significantly less than others). Or, the printer is blurry? 🤔  DRIVE-IN means you have FREE parking available. There is no drive around the venue, or any windows with Headset Staff asking you for your order.  NOTE: Real Working Men (mostly single) eat here! Lunch Service can be intense.  I look forward to taste testing the entire menu!  That Onion Ring looked very very good. 🤤
